headline: Agoda Spotlights Lantern Festivals Across Asia to Brighten the Year
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda is shining a light on some of Asia's most enchanting lantern festivals coming up in the remainder of the year. These lantern festivals are unmissable for travelers eager to immerse themselves in culture and dazzling light-filled celebrations.
